"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I have a friend who just started his own business, and he ran over and said to me,\\n\\nEntrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs 193\\n\\nNo longer, I no longer need to look at someone's face and work exclusively. I can do whatever I want, everyone has to listen to me! \\\"I just ditched him at the time to protect the people in your team who were against you. As a result, he may have just become a boss and was very excited and didn't take it seriously. The dignity of being a boss lasted only half a year, and then he went to work for someone again. NS.\\n\\nOf course, the purpose of antagonism is for the company's business. This is the prerequisite, and it is a matter of strategic level. However, at the tactical level, it is a good thing for someone to come out and argue against the design to the specific business development.\\n\\nBecause you, as the founder of the company, no matter how smart you are, it is impossible to fully understand the project and the market. He operates at the front line. If you are not at the front line, it will be difficult for you to understand the specific situation. If you decide on your own, the opinions of the people who need the front line operation must be carefully listened to. Everyone has blind spots. And these devilish people will help you further analyze what you have overlooked.\\n\\nDue to the influence of Chinese culture, we Chinese always have good face and are very reserved. For many things, you need to ask a few times before the other party can tell you the real reason. In addition, you are a superior. A lot of people just promise, that is, they have opinions and habitual reservations. This is very detrimental to entrepreneurship.\\n\\nA foreign scholar once did an experiment in which one person entered a team with five trustees. Six people measured a shorter rope and a slightly longer rope together, and then the five supporters said that the shorter one was actually longer. As a result, three-quarters of the people in the experiment accepted this. Wrong answer, and only a quarter of people insist on the truth and oppose these 5\\n\\nSupport. It can be seen how precious the people who really contradict the tune are. Since ancient times, there has been a saying in China that if you listen to both, you will be clear, and those who listen to it will be secret. Many faint monarchs in history are\\n\\nThe courtiers who rejected him sang the opposite, leading to the tragedy that the great country was overthrown. And those Mingjun, even like to hear the opposing opinions very much. Moreover, these people who always raise objections are active thinkers in the company. They are thinking about problems so they have objections. Can raise objections\\n\\n194 Entrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs\\n\\nSeeing proof is very attentive to the company's affairs. If you really fight in the market, you need such a person. This is also a manifestation of leadership. You can even train such a person to be a leader. Most people who do not raise objections are followers.\\n\\nWhen we do business, we pursue the objectivity, truth, and facts of the market. This kind of people who like to raise objections is to help us further analyze the truth of the market. Facts are really hard to come by.\\n\\nTherefore, I hope that the bosses will have the habit of protecting and cultivating the opponents in the team. As long as he is right and reasonable, and is for the company's overall business, he is worthy of praise and promotion. Don't reject people who disagree for the sake of your own face and sense of authority.\",\"timestamp\":1634801347,\"title\":\"Protect and train the opponents in the team\"},\"digest\":\"kT-EWGHab2qCN9vBiN35VnVyNfAuuDjFDG7H_OC7AGQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0500e3b6f7b1214a11851b9B348020C08018403b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"C_mSJf2s-iQwZ8r0vBXFQVMEyeKHuiDImYztzGjZlYUDtr9KuPfwld2zpcdbN5zVdSV_Wv4ZeG5TL052_7EzAQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1c6f856baad7dbcdc04a289cfb8c27fd2d4c254469eae7a6d5e283ce19250e091ab85676074d27b49e23c7d4b78b5f81e8536a0da448b30920c0f4dc5a6602e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"kT-EWGHab2qCN9vBiN35VnVyNfAuuDjFDG7H_OC7AGQ\"}"